title: Dutch Treat Update A161-165 (Rare Hits Project)
description:
From the Rare Hits Project: Five new 1-hour Dutch Treat Playlists. All in HQ.

A short time ago I run against the Rare Hits from the 80s vol 62. Good music from the Pre Indie period in which the electronic music was awakening (New Wave). A bit under the surface but not less interesting.

With many thanks to the original creator of the Rare Hits series, enjoy,
